<p><a name="Languages_using_bi-directional_text" id="Languages_using_bi-directional_text"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bi-directional_text&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Languages using bi-directional text">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Languages using bi-directional text</span></h2>
<p>There are very few <a href="/wiki/Writing_system" title="Writing system">scripts</a> that can be written in either direction.</p>
<p>Such was the case with <a href="/wiki/Egyptian_language" title="Egyptian language">Egyptian</a> <a href="/wiki/Egyptian_hieroglyph" title="Egyptian hieroglyph" class="mw-redirect">hieroglyphics</a>, where the signs had a distinct "head" that faced the beginning of a line and "tail" that faced the end.</p>
<p><a href="/wiki/Chinese_characters" title="Chinese characters" class="mw-redirect">Chinese characters</a> can also be written in either direction, especially in signs (but the orientation of the individual characters is never changed). This can often be seen on tour buses in China, where the company name customarily runs from the front of the vehicle to its rear - that is, from right to left on the right side of the bus, and from left to right on the left side of the bus.</p>
<table class="gallery" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 28px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Yangzhou-tour-bus--right-side-3182.jpg" class="image" title="Yangzhou-tour-bus--right-side-3182.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5a/Yangzhou-tour-bus--right-side-3182.jpg/120px-Yangzhou-tour-bus--right-side-3182.jpg" width="120" height="90" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p>The right side (text runs from right to left)</p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 28px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Yangzhou-tour-bus--leftt-side-3184.jpg" class="image" title="Yangzhou-tour-bus--leftt-side-3184.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/00/Yangzhou-tour-bus--leftt-side-3184.jpg/120px-Yangzhou-tour-bus--leftt-side-3184.jpg" width="120" height="90" border="0" /></a></div>
