<li><a href="http://bidi.info/" class="external text" title="http://bidi.info/" rel="nofollow">Bidirectional Scripts in Desktop Software</a> Working group for supporting BiDi in <a href="/wiki/Free_Software" title="Free Software" class="mw-redirect">Free Software</a>. Contains several links to readings and implementation regarding BiDi in <a href="/wiki/Computer" title="Computer">computer</a> systems.</li>
<li><a href="http://mac.plonter.co.il/plonwiki/BidiWiki" class="external text" title="http://mac.plonter.co.il/plonwiki/BidiWiki" rel="nofollow">Another Wiki about BiDi</a></li>
